snippet: Luminaries from the film, music and writing worlds honored Tom Waits and folk singer John Prine for their songwriting at the Song Lyrics of Literary Excellence Awards on Monday. Waits' wife, Kathleen Brennan, also was honored....
lead_paragraph: Luminaries from the film, music and writing worlds honored Tom Waits and folk singer John Prine for their songwriting at the Song Lyrics of Literary Excellence Awards on Monday. Waits' wife, Kathleen Brennan, also was honored.

headline.main: Tom Waits, His Wife, John Prine Receive Songwriting Awards
headline.print_headline: Tom Waits, His Wife, John Prine Receive Songwriting Awards
